    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find that has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single blemish, scratch, or dent, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth-running engine and a transmission that shifts flawlessly. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, operates exactly as it did when it first rolled off the lot. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been cared for with the utmost attention to detail, offering the next owner a brand-new driving experience.",
