    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative example, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle exhibits impeccable bodywork and a pristine interior, free from the typical signs of use. Engineered for the most discerning enthusiast, it offers a rare combination of mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. This is an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled caliber.",
      "price": 48900.0,
