    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute gem and has been pampered like a member of the family. It's in flawless condition and drives like a total dream! I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system that has been meticulously overhauled. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is superlative, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Finished in a deep Carbon Black with a flawless Nappa leather interior, this specimen exhibits zero drivetrain lash or suspension deflection. All bushings, cooling system components, and rod bearings have been serviced to factory tolerances, offering a turn-key experience for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. No accidents. Flawless interior. Mechanically perfect.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since the day it left the showroom. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the depth of the original paint without a single swirl mark, rock chip, or door ding. The wheels are free of any curb rash, wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show zero signs of bolster wear, the dash is free of UV damage, and the original factory floor mats have been preserved under protective layering. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a complete, binder-organized service history documenting every oil change and preventative maintenance milestone performed exclusively by certified master technicians. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions perfectly. It drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered\u2014tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
