      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the meticulously maintained interior, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
